<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy — SpaceHub India" %>

<div class="container py-5" style="max-width:760px;">
  <h1 class="fw-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-muted small mb-5">Last updated: March 2025</p>

  <p>SpaceHub India ("we", "our", "us") is committed to protecting your personal information. This policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your data.</p>

  <h5 class="fw-semibold mt-4">Information We Collect</h5>
  <ul>
    <li>Account details: name, email, phone number, city</li>
    <li>Booking information: dates, times, payment confirmations</li>
    <li>Content you upload: listing photos, reviews</li>
    <li>Usage data: pages visited, search queries</li>
  </ul>

  <h5 class="fw-semibold mt-4">How We Use Your Information</h5>
  <ul>
    <li>To process and confirm bookings</li>
    <li>To communicate about your account and bookings</li>
    <li>To improve the platform and personalise your experience</li>
    <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
  </ul>

  <h5 class="fw-semibold mt-4">Data Storage & Security</h5>
  <p>Files and photos are stored on Amazon S3 with encryption at rest. We use industry-standard SSL/TLS for all data in transit. Payments are processed by Razorpay and Stripe — we never store card details.</p>

  <h5 class="fw-semibold mt-4">Your Rights</h5>
  <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data at any time by contacting us at privacy@spacehub.in.</p>

  <h5 class="fw-semibold mt-4">Contact</h5>
  <p>Questions about this policy? Email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@spacehub.in">privacy@spacehub.in</a>.</p>
</div>
